name: Aclara Resources Inc.
longDescription: Aclara Resources Inc is a development-stage rare earth mineral resources company with approximately 451585 hectares of mining concessions located in the Maule Nuble Biobio and Araucan a regions of Chile. It is focused on the development and on the future construction and operation of the Penco Module which aims to produce a rare earth concentrate through a processing plant that will be fed by clays from nearby deposits.
